      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRE ISLAND (1) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 1.5 lengths from the winner SPRING LAYLA (20.84) at this track. One of the leading chances. MIDNIGHT GHOST (8) proved too good on debut over 365m at this track to score by 5.5 lengths (20.79). Boxed wide but has the pace to be prominent. Harder here but expected to measure up. MIDNIGHT SMOKE (5) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only one length (20.81) behind SPRING LAYLA at this track. Has good box speed and can overcome the tricky draw. Expected to be in the finish again. FAST RETURNS (2) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when third (21.31) at this track in a Maiden.",
